---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Über mich" description="Tobias Oberrauch — KI-Beauftragter bei audius, Software Engineer aus Holzmaden. Elterngruppenleiter für hochbegabte Kinder beim LVH Baden-Württemberg. Kontakt und Projekte.">
  <section class="page-header reveal">
    <div class="page-badge reveal reveal-delay-1">Persönlich</div>
    <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-2">Über mich</h1>
  </section>

  <div class="about-layout">
    <!-- Intro with avatar -->
    <div class="about-hero reveal reveal-delay-3">
      <img src="/images/tobias-audius.webp" alt="Tobias Oberrauch — KI-Beauftragter bei audius" class="portrait-photo" width="96" height="96" />
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <h2 class="hero-name">Tobias Oberrauch</h2>
        <p class="hero-title">KI-Beauftragter bei audius</p>
        <p class="hero-location">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
          Holzmaden, Baden-Württemberg
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main content grid -->
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-main">
        <section class="about-section reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <h2>Beruflich</h2>
          <p>
            Als <strong>KI-Beauftragter bei <a href="https://www.audius.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener">audius</a></strong>
            verantworte ich den verantwortungsvollen Einsatz künstlicher Intelligenz im Unternehmen.
            Dabei stehen ethische Aspekte, Datenschutz und Innovationskraft im Fokus —
            für nachhaltige und sichere KI-Lösungen.
          </p>
          <p>
            Meine Schwerpunkte liegen in RAG-Systemen, lokalen LLMs, Text-Klassifikation
            und dem Aufbau souveräner KI-Infrastruktur. Ich bin überzeugt, dass KI nur dann
            Vertrauen verdient, wenn sie transparent, privat und unter eigener Kontrolle läuft.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section reveal reveal-delay-5">
          <h2>Hochbegabung &amp; Engagement</h2>
          <p>
            Seit Januar 2026 leite ich gemeinsam mit meiner Frau <strong>Arkan</strong> die
            <a href="https://lvh-bw.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Elterngruppe Nürtingen / Kirchheim-Teck</a>
            des Landesverbands Hochbegabung Baden-Württemberg. Dort organisieren wir
            regelmäßige Spielenachmittage und bauen ein lokales Netzwerk für Familien
            hochbegabter Kinder auf.
          </p>
          <p>
            Das Thema Hochbegabung liegt mir am Herzen, weil ich aus eigener Erfahrung weiß,
            wie wichtig es ist, dass Kinder in ihrer Einzigartigkeit gesehen und gefördert werden.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section reveal reveal-delay-6">
          <h2>Was ich hier mache</h2>
          <ul class="what-list">
            <li>
              <span class="what-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 014 4v14a3 3 0 00-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 00-4 4v14a3 3 0 013-3h7z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span>Recherchen und Artikel zu Hochbegabung teilen</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="what-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span>Prototypen und interaktive Visualisierungen bauen</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="what-icon">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span>Technische Experimente dokumentieren und Open Source beitragen</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="about-sidebar">
        <div class="sidebar-card reveal reveal-delay-4">
          <h3>Steckbrief</h3>
          <dl class="steckbrief">
            <dt>Rolle</dt>
            <dd>KI-Beauftragter</dd>
            <dt>Firma</dt>
            <dd><a href="https://www.audius.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener">audius</a></dd>
            <dt>Standort</dt>
            <dd>Holzmaden</dd>
            <dt>Ehrenamt</dt>
            <dd>EG-Leiter LVH-BW</dd>
            <dt>Auf GitHub seit</dt>
            <dd>2010</dd>
            <dt>Repos</dt>
            <dd>97+</dd>
            <dt>Follower</dt>
            <dd>6.200+ (LinkedIn)</dd>
          </dl>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card reveal reveal-delay-5">
          <h3>Technologien</h3>
          <div class="tech-tags">
            <span>Python</span>
            <span>TypeScript</span>
            <span>Rust</span>
            <span>Astro</span>
            <span>RAG</span>
            <span>Ollama</span>
            <span>LLMs</span>
            <span>Claude</span>
            <span>Angular</span>
            <span>SQLite</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card reveal reveal-delay-6">
          <h3>Projekte</h3>
          <ul class="project-list">
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/tobiasoberrauch/rag-showcase" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <strong>rag-showcase</strong>
                <span>RAG-Demonstration</span>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/tobiasoberrauch/ollama-monitor" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <strong>ollama-monitor</strong>
                <span>Terminal-Monitor für Ollama</span>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://github.com/tobiasoberrauch/parameter-golf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                <strong>parameter-golf</strong>
                <span>Kleinstes LM-Training</span>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact section -->
    <section class="contact-section scroll-reveal">
      <h2>Kontakt</h2>
      <div class="contact-cards">
        <a href="mailto:tobias.oberrauch@gmx.de" class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="M22 4L12 13L2 4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="contact-label">E-Mail</div>
            <div class="contact-value">tobias.oberrauch@gmx.de</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/tobiasoberrauch" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="contact-label">GitHub</div>
            <div class="contact-value">@tobiasoberrauch</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="https://de.linkedin.com/in/tobiasoberrauch" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="contact-card">
          <div class="contact-icon">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="contact-label">LinkedIn</div>
            <div class="contact-value">Tobias Oberrauch</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .page-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 99px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  /* Hero intro */
  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .portrait-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 96px;
    height: 96px;
    border-radius: 22px;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--color-accent-glow);
    border: 3px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
  }

  .hero-location {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Grid layout */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .about-section p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
  }
  .about-section strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .what-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .what-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .what-list li:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .what-icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: flex;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* Sidebar */
  .sidebar-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .sidebar-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .steckbrief {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.4rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .steckbrief dt {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .steckbrief dd {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .steckbrief dd a {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .tech-tags span {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .tech-tags span:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .project-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .project-list li a {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    transition: all var(--transition);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .project-list li a:hover {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }
  .project-list li a strong {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .project-list li a span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  /* Contact */
  .contact-section h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .contact-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    transition: all var(--transition);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .contact-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .contact-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    background: var(--color-accent-light);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 10px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: all var(--transition);
  }
  .contact-card:hover .contact-icon {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
  }

  .contact-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }
  .contact-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px; gap: 2rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-sidebar { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .sidebar-card { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .contact-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .about-hero { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1rem; }
    .about-sidebar { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .contact-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
